<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSlack1983">Slack, Andy (December 1983). "Open Box: Traveller Starter Edition". <i>White Dwarf</i> (Games Workshop) (Issue 48): 10. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0265-8712" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0265-8712" rel="nofollow">0265-8712</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Open+Box%3A+Traveller+Starter+Edition&amp;rft.jtitle=White+Dwarf&amp;rft.aulast=Slack&amp;rft.aufirst=Andy&amp;rft.au=Slack%2C+Andy&amp;rft.date=December+1983&amp;rft.issue=Issue+48&amp;rft.pages=10&amp;rft.pub=Games+Workshop&amp;rft.issn=0265-8712&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Traveller_(role-playing_game)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSmith1996">Smith, Lester (1996). <i>Milieu 0</i>. Imperium Games. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0578283361" class="internal">ISBN 0-57828-336-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Milieu+0&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Lester&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Lester&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.pub=Imperium+Games&amp;rft.isbn=0-57828-336-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Traveller_(role-playing_game)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFWiseman1981"><a href="/wiki/Loren_Wiseman" title="Loren Wiseman">Wiseman, Loren K.</a> (1981). <i>Traveller Book 0: An Introduction To</i>. Game Designers' Workshop.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Traveller+Book+0%3A+An+Introduction+To&amp;rft.aulast=Wiseman&amp;rft.aufirst=Loren+K.&amp;rft.au=Wiseman%2C+Loren+K.&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft.pub=Game+Designers%27+Workshop&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Traveller_(role-playing_game)"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
